Kristen Bieniewicz of Westland has filed a $51 million lawsuit against Bassel Saad who is in prison for throwing a punch that killed her husband during a game last summer . 
  The figure represents $1 million for each of the 51 additional years he could have lived after he was punched in the head by Saad . 
  Kristen Bieniewski is suing Saad and another man who controlled the team and the soccer league . 
  Saad was recently sentenced to at least eight years in prison after pleading guilty to involuntary manslaughter . 
 